To find your office's existing retention schedule, go to the <a class="extLink" href="https://cms.byui.edu/home/Library/retention/Retention%20Schedules" title="Retention Schedule Library" target="_blank">Retention Schedule Library</a>.<br /><br />Links to the Departmental Retention Schedule, Records Transfer List, Records Destruction Form, and the Retention Schedule Library will allow you&nbsp;to fill out an online form or view and download your retention schedule. To complete a form, select the appropriate link, authenticate using your BYU-I username and password, and select <em>Add document</em> or at the top of the page click <em>Documents</em> then <em>New Document</em> (see below). <br /><br /><img alt="Creating a new form" height="261" src="Images/records-retention/newForm.png" title="New Form" width="453" /><br /><br />Upon completing a form, contact us and we'll assist you in destuction or transfer of your records. If you do not have access to the Retention Schedule Library or one of the forms listed above, <a class="intLink" href="x46348.xml" title="Contacts"><span style="color: #0066cc;">contact us</span></a>.]]></BodyCopy><xPower Type="GroupStart" Name="PageComponents" label="Page Components" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false" Expanded="" GroupStart=""><xPower Type="List" Name="OptionalColumnComponent" label="Optional Column Components" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false" Expanded="" List=""><xPower Type="Component" Component="" Name="Optional" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false" CompTypes="FacebookComponent;Image;ColumnTextComponent;Media;Quote" Expanded="false"/></xPower><xPower Type="Component" Name="QuickLinksColumn1" label="QuickLinks Column 1" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false" Component="" CompTypes="QuickLinksComponent"/><xPower Type="Component" Name="QuickLinksColumn2" label="QuickLinks Column 2" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false" Component="" CompTypes="QuickLinksComponent"/><xP